<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>页面未找到 - BTC挖矿计算器</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #121212 0%, #1e2329 100%);
            color: #ffffff; 
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .error-container { 
            background: #2d2d2d; 
            border: 1px solid #444; 
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .error-code { 
            font-size: 6rem; 
            color: #f39c12; 
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .btn-warning { 
            background-color: #f39c12; 
            border-color: #f39c12;
            color: #000;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn-outline-light:hover { 
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            color: #000; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
                <div class="card error-container text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="error-code mb-4">404</div>
                        
                        
                        <h2 class="mb-3">页面未找到</h2>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-muted">抱歉，您访问的页面不存在或已被移动。请检查网址是否正确，或使用下面的链接返回主页。</p>
                        
                        
                        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-center">
                            <a href="/" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg me-md-2">
                                <i class="bi bi-house"></i> 
                                返回首页
                            </a>
                            <a href="/calculator" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">
                                <i class="bi bi-calculator"></i> 
                                挖矿计算器
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <small class="text-muted">
                                
                                如果问题持续存在，请联系技术支持
                                
                            </small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>